bio.openEndedText: Private Pilot.  Non-Smoker.  Neat freak with the better side of OCD.
2020 R8, 2019 S63AMG, 2011 Ram 3500, 2001 Turbo LS Camaro, 1993 TT LS Foxbody

Welcome!

Are you ready to embark on an unforgettable journey through the world of automobiles? Look no further! I am Damien, your trusted Turo host and a true car enthusiast. I have dedicated my life to the pursuit of automotive knowledge and want to share my passion with you.

But it's not just passion that sets me apart; it's my unwavering dedication to providing the perfect rental experience. When you rent a car from me, you can expect nothing less than exceptional service and attention to detail. I believe in going the extra mile to ensure that every aspect of your journey is flawless, from the moment you book to the time you return the keys.

Here's what you can expect when renting from me:

1. Immaculate Fleet: Each car in my collection is meticulously maintained and regularly serviced to ensure optimal performance and reliability. I take pride in offering vehicles that are in pristine condition, both inside and out.

2. Smooth and Transparent Booking Process: Renting a car should be a breeze. That's why I've streamlined the booking process to be quick, straightforward, and transparent. No hidden fees or surprises—just a seamless experience from start to finish.

3. Concierge-level Customer Service: Your satisfaction is my top priority. I am available around the clock to address any questions or concerns you may have. Whether it's providing local recommendations or assisting with any unexpected situations, I'm here to make your rental experience as smooth as possible.

4. Flexibility and Convenience: I understand that plans can change, and I'm here to accommodate you. Need to extend your rental? No problem. Have a specific pickup or drop-off request? I'll do my best to make it happen. Your convenience is of utmost importance to me.

So, whether you're a car enthusiast seeking an adrenaline rush or simply in need of reliable transportation, I invite you to join me on an unparalleled rental experience. 

Remember, it's not just about renting a car—it's about embracing the exhilaration that comes with every twist of the wheel.

Hello my name is Hunter and I am steadily growing my Turo fleet of Tesla vehicles in the Indianapolis, Indiana area. My vehicle fleet includes a Tesla Model 3 and Tesla Model Y. I hope you take the opportunity to rent from me and I am here to make everything go as smoothly as possible. Thanks!
Hello! We are Luxury Motor Rentals and we are thrilled to be hosting our luxurious fleet of vehicles to the Indianapolis area. We look forward to meeting you!

Hey there! 

Thanks for choosing to rent with us on Turo. I'm Rock, and I'll be your host during your trip. 

I want to make sure you have an amazing experience, so let me tell you a bit about myself and why you can trust me as a responsible and reliable host.

First off, I take great pride in providing clean and well-maintained vehicles for all my guests. Your comfort and safety are my top priorities, so you can expect a well-cared-for car.

I've been driving over 25 years and have a clean driving record. Safety is super important to me, so you can have peace of mind knowing that I'll take good care of you on the road.

If you have any questions or need assistance during your trip, don't hesitate to reach out. I'm here to help and make sure you have a smooth and enjoyable experience.

I'm also a big travel enthusiast, so if you need any recommendations or tips for your destination, feel free to ask. I love sharing my favorite spots and hidden gems!

Once again, thanks for choosing to rent with us. I'm excited to be your host and provide you with a fantastic Turo experience. 

Safe travels!

Thanks so much for looking at our vehicle options for your next trip! Melissa and I started Curated Luxury Auto, LLC in February of 2023 with 1 car. We had used Turo multiple times as guests but never dreamed we would become hosts. Fast forward to today and 18-20 cars on Turo and we have grown just a bit. We have grown because folks trusted us with their vehicle needs and we took that choice seriously. We try very hard to offer exceptional vehicles that match an exceptional experience all at an affordable price. Our experience and reputation has quickly made us the "go to" partner for luxury branded cars in the Indy market. We hope that we have the opportunity to show you what makes us different! We appreciate your support of our "Mom and Pop" business!
